// WORKING NAME: "Bone Shield" (placeholder — needs naming pass)
// Ability: death_strike
// Rarity: Epic
// Uniqueness: Exclusive — only one copy allowed.
//
// Effect: Behavior hook "bone_shield_on_kill".
//
// When acquired: talent/systems/apply.rs inserts ActiveHook("bone_shield_on_kill") on the player.
// When removed (merchant): ActiveHook is removed.
//
// Hook behavior (implemented in ability/hooks/bone_shield.rs, registered in AbilityPlugin):
//   Tracks kills from Death Strike in AbilityHookState("bone_shield_kill_count").
//   When count reaches bone_shield_kill_threshold (from ResolvedParams), resets counter,
//   grants the player a "bone_shield" component that absorbs the next incoming hit,
//   then removes itself.
//
// This hook is listed in death_strike.ron under hooks: [(Post, "bone_shield_on_kill")].
// It fires after each Death Strike execution, but only if ActiveHook is present.
(
    id: "death_strike_bone_shield_epic",
    display_name: "Bone Shield",
    ability_scope: Some("death_strike"),
    rarity: Epic,
    uniqueness: Exclusive,
    effect: Behavior("bone_shield_on_kill"),
)
